Monk could do that as long as nothing is within agro range, no problem.
<br />

<br />
As long as you have done NO actual damage, if you are far enough away they will stick to your pet.
<br />
Note (because someone posted about doing this before): Never try to get an ex-pet to stick on a new one, it won't.  It will only agro you, or someone else who manages to taunt it off you, and that will never be your pet.</span></td>
